<doc id="438144" wikidata="Q744602" url="?curid=438144" title="Lagos, Pyrénées-Atlantiques">
<text>Lagos (; ) is a commune in the Pyrénées-Atlantiques department in south-western France.

==See also==
*Communes of the Pyrénées-Atlantiques department

